reviewText: This video is awesome. Styles P and new Hot talented artists performs hip-hop at a club in NYC with hot music videos and interviews. I love The Spot Review show! It's like a breath of fresh air. If you are tired of seeing the same faces in the music industry on TV, you need to check out this show.
